'''Jesmin''' was a type of [[Ocean/Legends|ocean]] [[Plant/Legends|kelp]] native to [[Dac/Legends|Dac]]. It was gathered for use as an ingredient in incense and perfumes.

It was also a common name among female [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]].<ref name="GCG">''[[Galactic Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

